      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or dents, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car performs perfectly, offering a smooth and powerful driving experience as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle with zero compromises in quality or performance.",
