    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that won't break the bank? This car is a fantastic choice! It's in honest, fair condition and has been a dependable companion on the road. While it shows some expected wear from its journeys, it still has plenty of miles left to give and offers a smooth, solid ride. It's the perfect opportunity to get a high-quality model at a great value!",
