      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a brand-new home. This car has been super reliable for me and is still in great shape for all your daily commutes or fun weekend road trips! It runs smoothly, has been well-loved, and is ready to hit the road today. If you're looking for a solid, dependable vehicle that\u2019s a total joy to drive, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
