    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for car that is ready for the road. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, showing only the minor, inevitable stone chips on the front fascia from highway driving. The body panels are straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, though there is some light, natural creasing on the driver's seat bolster. All electronic features, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car performs beautifully with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced at regular intervals. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is an honest, dependable vehicle that looks great and drives even better.",
      "price": 32500.0,
